ivardefs.name: comment
ivardefs.desc: Notes about the past or intended usage of this identifier.

ivardefs.name: period
ivardefs.desc: Identifies the period of time over which this identifier is considered appropriate to refer to the naming system.  Outside of this window, the identifier might be non-deterministic.

ivardefs.name: preferred
ivardefs.desc: Indicates whether this identifier is the "preferred" identifier of this type.

ivardefs.name: type
ivardefs.desc: Identifies the unique identifier scheme used for this particular identifier.

ivardefs.name: value
ivardefs.desc: The string that should be sent over the wire to identify the code system or identifier system.

properties.desc: Indicates how the system may be identified when referenced in electronic exchange.
